empo di rinascita, i suoi semi mettono radici._#','#_何年もの間塩と爪とに痛めつけられた彼は、歩むことと種撒くことを止めてしまった。 彼の撒いた種が根を張るのは、この再誕の今だけだ。_#',NULL,NULL,'#_Golpeado y maltratado por años de sal y garras, nunca dejó de caminar ni de sembrar. Recién ahora, en este momento de renacimiento, sus semillas germinan._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('247179','Malfegor','CMD','Legendary Creature — Demon Dragon','M','{2}{B}{B}{R}{R}','6','6','6',NULL,'Flying£When Malfegor enters the battlefield, discard your hand. Each opponent sacrifices a creature for each card discarded this way.','#_A demon cannot be trusted, and a dragon will not be ruled._#',NULL,'Jason Chan','208','3.263','£11/17/2017: Malfegor’s ability is not optional. You must discard your entire hand no matter how many creatures your opponents control.£11/17/2017: After you discard your hand and the number of creatures each opponent must sacrifice has been determined, each opponent in turn order, starting with the player whose turn it is if that player is your opponent, chooses which creatures they will sacrifice, then all the chosen creatures are all sacrificed at the same time.','RB (O)',NULL,'0.42','1.22','2.03',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'BR',NULL,NULL,'Malfégor','Malfegor','Malfegor','マルフェゴール',NULL,NULL,'Malfegor',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Créature légendaire : démon et dragon','Legendäre Kreatur — Dämon, Drache','Creatura Leggendaria — Demone Drago','伝説のクリーチャー ― デーモン・ドラゴン',NULL,NULL,'Criatura legendaria — Dragón demonio',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Vol£Quand Malfégor arrive sur le champ de bataille, défaussez-vous de votre main. Chaque adversaire sacrifie une créature pour chaque carte défaussée de cette manière.','Fliegend£Wenn Malfegor ins Spiel kommt, wirf alle Karten aus deiner Hand ab. Jeder Gegner opfert für jede auf diese Weise abgeworfene Karte eine Kreatur.','Volare£Quando Malfegor entra nel campo di battaglia, scarta la tua mano. Ogni avversario sacrifica una creatura per ogni carta scartata in questo modo.','飛行